title: 19 Doctors from Mexican Hospital Test Positive for Coronavirus
description: Mexican officials confirmed that 19 doctors from one hospital tested positive to the novel Coronavirus (COVID-19). Health leaders claim all were infected outside the hospital and therefore should not considered an outbreak scenario.
